description:
Give the gift of new taste experiences to your loved ones or indulge yourself in irresistible flavours.

Never run out of tasty recipe ideas with the bestselling Tweed Real Food Avo Smash Gourmet Gift Hamper. 'Smash' every recipe including avocados and more. From the most delicious Guacamole to smashed avo on toast, everything will taste as good as if you ordered it in a cafe or restaurant!

The Avo Smash Gourmet Gift Hamper includes:
- Bourbon Maple Splash Balsamic Vinegar, 250ml
- Avo Smash Dukkah, 60g
- Lime Pepper Grinder Salt, 70g
- Stainless Steel Manual Grinder
- Printed Recipe Card
name: Tweed Real Food 1EA
